N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 641.7 - Final dates for filing

State Regulations

Every telephone corporation shall file, in accordance with
the requirements of section
3.5
of this Title, each annual
report as soon as possible after the end of the year covered by the report, but
in no event later than the date specified herein. The final dates for filing
shall be as follows: Kind of Utility

Filing Date

Telephone Corporations

March 31
